WEBVTT

00:16:28.098 --> 00:16:30.248
And he said, "Oh, even if there was nothing,

00:16:30.248 --> 00:16:32.244
you still wouldn't be satisfied."

00:16:32.244 --> 00:16:35.993
So — (Laughter) — okay.

00:16:35.993 --> 00:16:38.355
So you're not astonished. I don't care.

00:16:38.355 --> 00:16:41.328
But I will tell you something to conclude

00:16:41.328 --> 00:16:43.606
that I guarantee you will astonish you,

00:16:43.606 --> 00:16:46.273
because it's astonished all of the brilliant,

00:16:46.273 --> 00:16:48.586
wonderful people I've met at this TED conference,

00:16:48.586 --> 00:16:50.800
when I've told them, and it's this:

00:16:50.800 --> 00:16:55.302
Never in my life have I had a cell phone.

00:16:55.302 --> 00:16:57.179
Thank you.

00:16:57.179 --> 00:17:01.179
(Laughter) (Applause)